OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy through much of
OL,6,Fthe morning, though brightening later
OL,7,Fin the day. The odd spot of rain
OL,8,Fcannot be ruled out, especially over
OL,9,Fhills and near eastern coasts. Windy
OL,10,Fand cool over hills, breezy and warmer
OL,11,Felsewhere.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy through the evening
OL,14,Fand overnight, with outbreaks of light
OL,15,Frain possible at times. Windy over
OL,16,Fhills and coasts, breezy elsewhere.
OL,17,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
