OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day,
OL,6,Fespecially across western hills. A
OL,7,Fchance of some light rain late
OL,8,Fmorning. Sunny intervals developing in
OL,9,Fthe east later in the day. Winds
OL,10,Feasing. Warm.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,13,Fand sunny to end the week. Light
OL,14,Fwinds, though breezier across hills
OL,15,Fand for most on Friday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fincreasing, becoming very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
